						               													<description>PubliCity is a worker placement euro-game, in which all players are owners of their own advertising agency, in the first decades of the 20th century.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During the match, all will dispute to make their agencies, and clients, the most famous brands of the region. Play as Abraham, Eli, Henry, or Victoria, and manage an advertising agency with unique expertise.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Offer your services to 7 different clients, and discover the best way to attend to their needs, by announcing on newspaper, outdoors, flyers, or by participating in regional events.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the end of the last round, the player with the greatest amount of victory points wins the game. These points can be achieved by succeeding in marketing campaigns, building new branches, and standing out at events.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher (translated)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;PubliCidade &amp;eacute; um jogo de tabuleiro no estilo euro, para 2-4 participantes, no qual os jogadores s&amp;atilde;o donos de ag&amp;ecirc;ncias de propaganda nos EUA do in&amp;iacute;cio do s&amp;eacute;culo XX.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Durante a partida, todos disputar&amp;atilde;o para tornarem suas ag&amp;ecirc;ncias e seus clientes as marcas mais famosas e bem-sucedidas da regi&amp;atilde;o. Jogue com Abraham, Eli, Henry ou Victoria, e gerencie empresas com especialidades &amp;uacute;nicas, alocando trabalhadores, fazendo melhorias na ag&amp;ecirc;ncia e usando habilidades especiais.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Ofere&amp;ccedil;a seus servi&amp;ccedil;os para 7 clientes diferentes, descobrindo a melhor forma de atender suas necessidades. Anuncie em jornais, distribua panfletos, construa outdoors, participe de eventos, e dispute os melhores contratos ao longo de um per&amp;iacute;odo de 6 meses-rodadas.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;No final, a ag&amp;ecirc;ncia com a maior quantidade de pontos de reconhecimento ser&amp;aacute; a vitoriosa. Estes pontos podem ser adquiridos realizando campanhas de marketing, obtendo destaque em eventos, construindo novas filiais, ou fidelizando clientes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
